messages.text: Yeah! Bought my first lotto ticket ever and won like a million dollars!!!!
Can’t. I’m at the store right now cashing it in
They’re not gonna give you a million dollars at the store
I still gotta cash it in
Did you do your essay for Mrs. Jacob’s class that’s due tomorrow?
I brought it with me. To do during breaks
That’s what I was gonna do mine on
Will you write it for me?
And you’ll give it to me when?
As soon as they give me the check
I can’t believe you asked me that
ASS! My boss just caught me texting!
So leave and do my essay
You won’t need that fast food job with 10 grand in ur pocket!!!
I don’t have the numbers anymore stupid! I just told you. Haha
Fo’ sho’ I got you! 10 grand man!!!
OK. I just told my boss to suck it!!! Hahahaha!!!!
On my way to ur house
No, I got a lot going on
After I leave the store I gotta test drive a Ferrari, look for a mansion
Plus my mom’s bugging me to pay off her house
Really? You won’t help her out?
But I told her I got other people to take care of
Then my whole family keeps blowing me up, wanting stuff
I can’t believe I’m getting $10,000 to do ur homework again lol
What do you want your essay to be about?
You just want to use mine then?
Yeah, I got another topic in mind
Just put the essay under the door mat
Cause I’m at the Ferrari dealers
You sure ur not at home???
Yeah, I’m not there. So I don’t know how u can see my car
You’re not just sitting in ur room?
C’mon. Go downstairs and open the door
Did you really win the lotto?
Just slide the essay under the door
You’re not trying to trick me again?
Then come downstairs and let me in
I’m not leaving till you show me the lotto ticket
I told you I don’t have it!!!
Maybe I’ll key ur car then
Since you’re not even here. Haha!
I can tell. I’m looking out the window in my room
I parked behind the tree, dummy
So u can’t see it from ur room
But ur mom’s just getting home
Maybe I’ll tell her I quit my job b/c of you!!
No!! DON’T!! She’ll take away my car!!!!
So u didn’t win the lottery???!!!
I’ll make it up to you. I promise
Gotcha!!! I’m still at work, dumbass
I knew u had to be at home
And I wasn’t gonna fall for your BS again. Hahaha
